headline: Is Carnival (CCL) Still Attractive After Its Recent Share Price Rebound?
summary: If you are wondering whether Carnival Corporation & at around US$30.18 is still good value after its rebound, you are not alone. The stock has seen a 6% decline over the last 7 days, a 5.5% gain over 30 days, is down 2.4% year to date, yet is up 21% over 1 year and has a very large 3 year return that is close to 2x, as well as a 45.2% gain over 5 years.
